# AgentVault
## Autonomous Agent Economy on Filecoin · Tracks 1 + 4
**PRD v1.0 · March 2026**

---

## The 3-Line Pitch

**AgentVault** gives AI agents a complete economic life on Filecoin — they store data, earn from it, and die when their budget runs out.

Watch it live: a neural network of agents pulses across your screen, edges light up when USDFC flows, nodes dim and disappear when agents go broke.

The dashboard is not decoration — it is the proof that autonomous agent economies work onchain.

---

## Why Track 1 + Track 4 Together

| Alone | Together |
|-------|---------|
| Track 1: "Here's an SDK" — judges have seen a thousand SDKs | The SDK is the engine. The economy is the proof the engine works. |
| Track 4: "Here's a demo" — no reusable artifact | Same codebase. Judges for Track 1 see clean API + docs. Judges for Track 4 see agents living and dying in real time. |

**Submit to both tracks. One repo. Explicitly state it in the README.**

