### 1.6 The Visual Aesthetic — Design Decision

**Dark neural network. High contrast. Green/blue/amber on near-black.**

- Background: `#080c14` — almost black, slight blue tint (not pure black — it reads as "space", not "broken")
- Font: `JetBrains Mono` — monospace throughout. Terminal energy. Every number looks exact.
- No rounded cards. No shadows. No gradients. Raw edges. Data first.
- The graph is 75% of the screen. Everything else is secondary.
- Dead agents don't disappear — they become **grey ghosts** that stay in the graph. The network remembers who died.

