## 6. Project Structure

One repository: **StorKeep** ships the SDK and the web app together (Agent Vault is the `/economy` experience inside the app, not a second Next.js project).

```
storkeep/                              ← repo root
├── storkeep-sdk/                      ← Track 1: npm `storkeep-sdk` (AgentVault, Synapse, Pin)
│   └── src/
│       ├── index.ts
│       └── agent/                     AgentVault.ts, synapse.ts, filecoin-pin.ts, policies.ts, …
│
├── storkeep-app/                      ← Track 4: Next.js — StorKeep + Agent Vault at `/economy`
│   ├── app/
│   │   ├── page.tsx
│   │   ├── economy/page.tsx          THE DASHBOARD — full-screen neural network
│   │   └── api/                      events, agents, economy start/stop, stats, listings, …
│   ├── next.config.mjs               redirects `/agentvault` → `/economy` (308)
│   ├── components/                   AgentNetwork, TxFeed, AgentPanel, SiteNav, …
│   ├── agents/                       producer, consumer, guardian, spawner
│   ├── lib/                          Prisma, event-bus, agent-wallet, …
│   ├── prisma/
│   └── vercel.json
│
└── storkeep-contracts/contracts/
    ├── AgentBudget.sol
    └── StorKeepRegistry.sol
```

