## 7. Demo Script — 4 Minutes

### Setup (before demo, invisible)

- 7 agents spawned on Calibration with different budgets
- 2 agents pre-killed (grey ghosts visible in graph from frame 1)
- Graph already running and pulsing when you share screen

### The Script

| Time | Action | What Judges See |
|------|--------|----------------|
| 0:00–0:20 | Open browser — deployed StorKeep app at `/economy` (e.g. `https://<your-app>.vercel.app/economy`) | Full-screen neural network already live. 7 nodes orbiting Filecoin hexagon. 2 grey ghosts. Edges pulsing. |
| 0:20–0:45 | Narrate the graph | "Green nodes are Producers — they grow as they store more data. Blue nodes are Consumers — they shrink as they spend. Orange diamonds are Guardians — they watch for dark CIDs. Grey nodes are dead agents — their data pruned, gone." |
| 0:45–1:15 | Click Consumer-1 (low budget, flashing red ring) | Agent panel slides in: budget 0.003 USDFC, 31% remaining, CRITICAL. Shows CIDs it's purchased, TX history, Filfox link. |
| 1:15–1:45 | Consumer-1 makes a retrieve — watch it live | Blue particle flows along edge from Consumer to Producer. Consumer node shrinks visibly. Producer node pulses green. TX feed updates: "Consumer-1 → Producer-2  0.003 USDFC". |
| 1:45–2:15 | Consumer-1 hits zero budget — AGENT DEATH | Node dims to grey, all edges fade simultaneously, "AGENT DIED" event fires in TX feed. Budget ring disappears. Grey ghost stays in graph. Filfox shows `AgentDied` event onchain. |
| 2:15–2:45 | Guardian detects a dark CID | Amber pulse along edge to Filecoin node. "Guardian-1 re-pinned bafyrei… 0.012 USDFC" in TX feed. Open Filecoin Pin dashboard — CID visible. |
| 2:45–3:15 | Open terminal — `npm install storkeep-sdk` | Live install. Show 8 lines of code. "This is all it takes to run an agent on Filecoin." |
| 3:15–4:00 | Show architecture diagram + Filecoin Calibration | Filfox showing live `DataStored`, `BudgetCharged`, `AgentDied` events. BaseScan showing USDFC payments. "Every action. Onchain. Verifiable." |

