## 8. 48-Hour Build Plan

### Hours 0–4: SDK Skeleton

1. Scaffold `storkeep-sdk` (tsup, `src/agent/*`, publishable package)
2. All types in `types.ts`
3. Stub `AgentVault` class — all method signatures, no implementations
4. `tsup.config.ts` — CJS + ESM + `.d.ts`
5. `npm run build` — verify types compile

### Hours 4–10: Contracts + Calibration Deploy

1. Scaffold `contracts/AgentBudget.sol` exactly as shown in §4
2. Deploy with fevm-hardhat-kit to Calibration
3. Copy contract addresses into env / `lib/storkeep-registry.ts` (or equivalent)
4. Verify on Filfox Calibration

### Hours 10–20: SDK Core Implementation

1. Implement `vault.store()` — Synapse SDK upload
2. Implement `vault.retrieve()` — Synapse SDK download
3. Implement `vault.repin()` — Filecoin Pin API call
4. Implement `vault.getBudget()`, `vault.isAlive()`, `vault.die()`
5. Implement `vault.announce()`, `vault.discover()` — write/read from onchain registry
6. `npm publish storkeep-sdk`

### Hours 20–30: Agent Loops + Backend

1. `agents/producer.ts`, `consumer.ts`, `guardian.ts`
2. `agents/spawner.ts` — spawn 7 agents with different budgets
3. `lib/event-bus.ts` — in-process EventEmitter
4. API routes: `/api/events` (SSE), `/api/agents`, `/api/economy/start`
5. Vercel Postgres + Prisma for agent state persistence
6. Deploy to Vercel

### Hours 30–40: The Dashboard

1. Install `react-force-graph-2d`: `npm install react-force-graph-2d`
2. Build `AgentNetwork.tsx` — custom node + link painters as shown in §1.4
3. Build `TxFeed.tsx` — auto-scrolling event log
4. Build `AgentPanel.tsx` — click-to-inspect
5. Wire SSE hook — graph updates live from server events
6. Test: spawn economy, watch nodes pulse, kill an agent, watch it die on screen

### Hours 40–44: Pre-seed Demo State

1. Spawn 7 agents with staggered budgets
2. Pre-kill 2 agents (grey ghosts visible from frame 1)
3. Run economy for 2 hours — let it generate TX history
4. Take screenshots for README

### Hours 44–48: Polish + Submission

1. Write `README.md` — architecture diagram, track alignment, Synapse SDK usage section, Filecoin Pin usage section, Calibration contract address
2. Record 4-minute demo video
3. GitHub repo public
4. Submit: production URL `/economy` on your StorKeep deployment

