## 9. `.env.example`

```bash
# ── Synapse SDK / Filecoin Onchain Cloud ──────────────────────────────
# Get from: https://docs.filecoin.cloud/getting-started/
# Fund with tUSDFC from Calibration faucet
FILECOIN_PRIVATE_KEY=0x_your_agent_wallet_private_key
FILECOIN_RPC_URL=https://api.calibration.node.glif.io/rpc/v1

# ── Filecoin Pin ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get from: https://pin.filecoin.cloud (register for alpha access)
FILECOIN_PIN_TOKEN=your_filecoin_pin_api_token

# ── AgentBudget.sol ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Deployed by you using fevm-hardhat-kit on Calibration
AGENT_BUDGET_CONTRACT=0x_deployed_contract_address

# ── Vercel Postgres (auto-injected after adding storage in dashboard)
POSTGRES_PRISMA_URL=postgresql://...
POSTGRES_URL_NON_POOLING=postgresql://...

# ── Economy Config ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Starting budgets for demo agents (USDFC, 6 decimals)
PRODUCER_BUDGET=10
CONSUMER_BUDGET_LOW=3        # will die fastest — good for demo
CONSUMER_BUDGET_MED=7
CONSUMER_BUDGET_HIGH=15
GUARDIAN_BUDGET=8

CYCLE_MS=8000                # agent action interval (8 seconds)
GUARDIAN_CYCLE_MS=15000      # guardian check interval

# ── Cron Secret (Vercel calls /api/cron with this) ──────────────────
# Generate: openssl rand -hex 32
CRON_SECRET=your_random_secret

# ── App ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=https://<your-storkeep-deployment>.vercel.app
```

